&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 芙蓉楼送辛渐
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 王昌龄
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
