loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="177"
data-flex-basis="426px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="定慧寺">定慧寺
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>焦山因东汉焦光隐居山中而得名。山中古寺定慧寺，也是千年宝刹。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://chengxiaqiucao.github.io/post/082-%E9%95%87%E6%B1%9F/IMG_6016.jpeg"
width="1536"
height="2048"
